appgateway_name.description: Name of your Application gateway. Will be prefixed and affixed.

key_vault_name.description: Name of your Key Vault. This will be prefixed and affixed.

location.description: Location for your resource group. Allowed locations: norwayeast, norwaywest, westeurope, northeurope

nsg_name.description: Name of your network security group. This will be prefixed and affixed.

prefix.description: Prefix for your resource group name.

resource_group_name.description: Resource group name. This will be prefixed and affixed.

sql_database_name.description: Name of your SQL database. This will be prefixed and affixed.

sql_login_object_id.description: Object ID of your AzureAD administrator. It is the object id found in Azure AD on the user object.

sql_login_username.description: Username of your SQL AzureAD administrator. Must be a full UPN.

sql_server_name.description: Name of your SQL server. This will be prefixed and affixed.

vm_name.description: Name of your virtual machine. This will be prefixed and shortened if needed (15 chars max including prefix and affix).

vnet_address_space.description: Address space for your virtual network. Defaults to 10.0.0.0/16.

vnet_name.description: Name for your virtual network. This will be prefixed and affixed.
